---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Start Here">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Start Here</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
        Welcome to Real & Raw Gospel. This is where your journey begins. No fluff, no religious traditions—just pure truth from the Word of YAHUAH.
      </p>
      
      <h2>First Things First</h2>
      <p>
        Before we dive deep into the meat of Scripture, you need to understand the foundation. The gospel is not about making you comfortable—it's about making you holy. It's about transformation through the RUACH HAQODESH.
      </p>
      
      <h2>The Sacred Names</h2>
      <p>
        Throughout this site, you'll see names like <strong>YAHUAH</strong>, <strong>YAHUSHA</strong>, and <strong>RUACH HAQODESH</strong>. These are the sacred names restored from the Hebrew Scriptures. We honor the Name above all names.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Teaching rooted in Scripture, not tradition</li>
        <li>A call to walk in holiness and obedience</li>
        <li>Training in spiritual warfare and the authority of believers</li>
        <li>Understanding the Feasts of YAHUAH and His appointed times</li>
        <li>Preparation for the end times and the return of YAHUSHA HAMASHIACH</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <p>
        We recommend you start by exploring these core sections:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 not-prose mt-6">
        <a href="/walk-in-the-spirit" class="block p-4 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 hover:border-blue-600 dark:hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Walk in the Spirit</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">Learn to live daily by the RUACH HAQODESH</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/identity-and-messiah" class="block p-4 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 hover:border-blue-600 dark:hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Identity & Mashiach</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">Discover who you are in YAHUSHA</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

